You are implementing a feature for the collabspace-server project (Spring Boot 3.4.5, Java 21).

## Task Description

Create 3 files to add a view type statistics endpoint that calls apitable's existing statistics API via Feign.

### Task 1: Create ApitableStatisticsFeign

Create file: `D:\project\pt-gitlab\collabspace\collabspace-server\src\main\java\com\yottastudios\ns\collabspace\third\feign\ApitableStatisticsFeign.java`

```java
package com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.third.feign;

import org.springframework.cloud.openfeign.FeignClient;
import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.GetMapping;

import lombok.Data;

@FeignClient(name = "apitableStatisticsFeign", url = "${apitable.host}")
public interface ApitableStatisticsFeign {

    @GetMapping("/api/v1/statistics/get")
    ResponseData<StatisticsData> getStatistics();

    @Data
    class ResponseData<T> {
        private Boolean success;
        private Integer code;
        private String message;
        private T data;
    }

    @Data
    class StatisticsData {
        private Long gridViewNum;
        private Long kanbanViewNum;
        private Long galleryViewNum;
        private Long calendarViewNum;
        private Long ganttViewNum;
        private Long architectureViewNum;
        private Long hierarchyViewNum;
        private String statisticsDay;
    }
}
```

### Task 2: Create ViewTypeStatisticsVo

Create file: `D:\project\pt-gitlab\collabspace\collabspace-server\src\main\java\com\yottastudios\ns\collabspace\workspace\vo\ViewTypeStatisticsVo.java`

```java
package com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.workspace.vo;

import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;
import lombok.Builder;
import lombok.Data;
import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;

import java.io.Serializable;

@Data
@Builder
@NoArgsConstructor
@AllArgsConstructor
public class ViewTypeStatisticsVo implements Serializable {
    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;

    /** 表格视图数 */
    private Long gridViewNum;
    /** 看板视图数 */
    private Long kanbanViewNum;
    /** 相册视图数 */
    private Long galleryViewNum;
    /** 日历视图数 */
    private Long calendarViewNum;
    /** 甘特视图数 */
    private Long ganttViewNum;
    /** 架构视图数 */
    private Long architectureViewNum;
    /** 层级视图数 */
    private Long hierarchyViewNum;
    /** 统计日期 */
    private String statisticsDay;
}
```

### Task 3: Modify SpaceNodeStatisticsController

Modify file: `D:\project\pt-gitlab\collabspace\collabspace-server\src\main\java\com\yottastudios\ns\collabspace\workspace\controller\SpaceNodeStatisticsController.java`

Add these imports at the top:
```java
import com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.third.feign.ApitableStatisticsFeign;
import com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.workspace.vo.ViewTypeStatisticsVo;
```

Add this field after the existing `@Resource` fields:
```java
@Resource
private ApitableStatisticsFeign apitableStatisticsFeign;
```

Add this method to the controller class:
```java
@GetResource(path = "/view/count", requiredPermission = false, requiredLogin = false)
@Operation(summary = "查询智能表格各视图类型的使用数量")
public ResponseData<ViewTypeStatisticsVo> getViewTypeStatistics() {
    ApitableStatisticsFeign.ResponseData<ApitableStatisticsFeign.StatisticsData> response =
            apitableStatisticsFeign.getStatistics();
    if (response == null || response.getData() == null) {
        return ResponseData.success(null);
    }
    ApitableStatisticsFeign.StatisticsData data = response.getData();
    ViewTypeStatisticsVo vo = ViewTypeStatisticsVo.builder()
            .gridViewNum(data.getGridViewNum())
            .kanbanViewNum(data.getKanbanViewNum())
            .galleryViewNum(data.getGalleryViewNum())
            .calendarViewNum(data.getCalendarViewNum())
            .ganttViewNum(data.getGanttViewNum())
            .architectureViewNum(data.getArchitectureViewNum())
            .hierarchyViewNum(data.getHierarchyViewNum())
            .statisticsDay(data.getStatisticsDay())
            .build();
    return ResponseData.success(vo);
}
```

## Context

- This is a Spring Boot project at `D:\project\pt-gitlab\collabspace\collabspace-server`
- The existing controller is at `src\main\java\com\yottastudios\ns\collabspace\workspace\controller\SpaceNodeStatisticsController.java`
- Follow the pattern from `ApitableMigrationFeign.java` (inner ResponseData class pattern)
- The controller uses `@ApiResource(path = "/node/statistics")` so the full path will be `/api/v1/node/statistics/view/count`
- Use `@GetResource` annotation (not `@GetMapping`) - this is the project's custom annotation
- `ResponseData` for the controller return is from `com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.core.support.ResponseData`

## Your Job

1. Create the 2 new files
2. Modify the existing controller
3. Do NOT commit - just write the code

Report back with status and files changed.

